| id                  | 5                                    |
| install_output      | text                                 |
| invprovision        | None                                 |
| location            | {}                                   |
| mgmt_ip             | None                                 |
| mgmt_mac            | 08:00:27:5c:97:db                    |
| operational         | disabled                             |
| personality         | compute                              |
| reserved            | False                                |
| rootfs_device       | sda                                  |
| serialid            | None                                 |
| software_load       | 15.10                                |
| task                | None                                 |
